cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote SCTP data port to 2153 will cause F1 data interface connectivity issues, preventing proper routing and data transmission, leading to configuration rejection.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Modifying the local N data port to 2153 will disrupt F1 data communication, leading to routing failures, connectivity issues, and system faults in the DU.
